4.3. Colors

  


Requirements

On all records of the main interface, the section heading colors will match the darker color green of the Symbiz logo. The color number (RGB) is "54, 89, 1". Note that the text color for labels on the headings is white instead of the standard black. 

  


All buttons on the main interface are gray instead of the standard blue color. This is to provide a more visually pleasing color combination, as the standard blue color clashes with the green.
